ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR RESEARCH AND POLICY USE:

This project contains research, analysis, and policy recommendations for urban 
transformation. While the code and methodology are provided under the MIT License, 

Users are encouraged to:

1. Cite this work appropriately in academic or policy publications
2. Acknowledge the original analysis when adapting the methodology for other cities
3. Share improvements and adaptations with the community
4. Respect the intent of this work: advancing sustainable urban development

For questions about the commercial use of the research findings or collaboration 
opportunities, please contact the project maintainers.

DATA DISCLAIMER:
The data and analysis provided are based on publicly available sources and 
research methodologies current as of 2025. Users should verify data accuracy 
and adapt methodologies as appropriate for their specific use cases.

POLICY DISCLAIMER:
This project presents research findings and recommendations. Implementation 
of any policies or projects should involve proper feasibility studies, 
stakeholder consultation, and compliance with local regulations.
